like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"講真，樓主你如果發出黎，我真係會報警，等警察上你屋企打個轉黎判斷你有冇犯法，我係認真，唔係講緊笑，你話我報警lun，正義lun，乜都好，隨便你。<br />\n<br />\n你有無想過你呢種一時之快會對當事人有幾大傷害？傳左出去人地點見人，張相仲要咁清？你地班友可能就睇得好happy，人地分分鐘就躲係屋企喊。人有時好脆弱，個女仔有乜事的話，你良心過唔過意得去？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我勸你放出黎之前三思一下，唔好受班花生友影響，呢度D人有野睇就唔會理他人感受，當中仲有成班小朋友字都未識得幾個，希望你可以作出獨立判斷，唔好助長網絡暴力，做埋晒D損人不利己的事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 你果度我冇睇錯係黃大仙黎，要搵你住邊計下角度就知，IP 都唔洗check"},{"pid":"39603a641ac9d97d4cac01e4c232fe1595a81555","tid":55334,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:46:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">雁詩</span>feel<br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de34c1bf29a615295190282473ae30f88fbea71a","tid":55334,"uid":69233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"之前買野已經留意到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n包禮物特登企左勁耐<br />\n樓主有圖好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c0eea04f5d91d40eae22bd0a366a520fe4aa4c","tid":55334,"uid":20110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:48:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9f1346c1f973cb002b6c9169731b329df888672","tid":55334,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"3c9590a0fd0ca68c57f2377c1fc2ef5abaf3bfb1","tid":55334,"uid":7835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:52:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人知包到幾時呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n好想俾佢瘋狂包禮物呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e817695d6a1632a19212bc65d